properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 27 at 9:00AM CST until January 27 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Corpus Christi TX
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one mile or less.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Baffin Bay to Port Aransas out 20
NM and Coastal waters from Port Aransas to Matagorda Ship
Channel out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until noon CST today.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL NOON CST TODAY
